        {
          "id": "grommet-top-guide",
          "title": "Grommet Top",
          "description": "Width = Rod/Track Width * Fullness/Number of Panels (2.0x Fullness is recommended)\n\nLength = 1.5 inches + Measure from the very top of the rod to the floor + Bottom\n\nDifferent Bottom Measurement\n\n1/2\" Above the Floor: -1/2\"\nKiss the Floor: 0\nPuddling: +2\"\n\nFor more puddling, add a longer bottom.",
